query:
INSERT INTO expeditions (guideId, trailId, title, startDate, endDate, price, capacity, status, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 
  (SELECT id FROM users WHERE userType = 'guide' LIMIT 1),
  (SELECT id FROM trails WHERE status = 'published' LIMIT 1),
  'Expedição Teste Mercado Pago',
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 30 DAY),
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 32 DAY),
  250.00,
  10,
  'active',
  NOW(),
  NOW();
